{"tid":427680,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"(幫星如平反) 唔識睇就唔好話人黑哨啦","createTime":"2017-10-07T15:09:21.000Z","updateTime":"2017-10-08T01:18:22.000Z","uid":38539,"like":71,"dislike":14,"uniUserReply":36,"replies":[{"pid":"fba8836c24a9b99f8a57a5e67f98bdea0bec73c2","tid":427680,"uid":38539,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-07T15:09:21.000Z","msg":"河野自己當時都認咗犯規用頭撞到星如隻眼嫁！<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/ZgfeSOJmsgM?t=31m5s\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FZgfeSOJmsgM%3Ft%3D31m5s&d=spwLGdFCjFoGnQp%2Fvj4Y2dtKgwQIhJBw7VlnLihElrQ%3D&h=4f1bec23\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/ZgfeSOJmsgM?t=31m5s</a><br />\n31:05<br />\n<br />\n其後裁判宣星如因傷無法繼續，終止比賽計點數都好合理。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n4.1.2 直到比賽結束前，評判員將為運動員每一回合進行評分，<br />\n根據記分系統統計分數，分數領先的運動員為獲勝方。<br />\n如果比賽提前終止，即使該回合不完整也必須評分。<br />\n<br />\n4.1.2.1 國際拳總公開拳擊比賽&ndash;如果因非故意犯規造成受傷，<br />\n導致台上裁判員終止比賽時，適用上述 4.1.2 規則；"},{"pid":"a6feaa03f46101954b052adf2037c2b3e805b539","tid":427680,"uid":38539,"like":3,"dislike":2,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-07T15:11:32.000Z","msg":"規則 6. 犯規<br />\n<br />\n6.1 犯規種類<br />\n<br />\n6.1.2 用頭部、肩部、前臂、肘關節頂撞或打擊對手，<br />\n用手臂或肘關節擠壓對手面部，把對手頭向後壓向圍繩。"},{"pid":"89c09329939a90359e37867e05c56b81aa448a1f","tid":427680,"uid":1734,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-07T15:12:02.000Z","msg":"你吓鳩粒清就叻"},{"pid":"ff27639b23a7740adc0573c7056fceab555da744","tid":427680,"uid":145923,"like":1,"dislike":19,"score":-18,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-07T15:13:19.000Z","msg":"咁既拳真係唔識睇<br />\n以後唔再睇唔再理香港拳場"},{"pid":"94fc289e2c71045dc62f2a143440b1a044d67da1","tid":427680,"uid":38539,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-07T15:16:56.000Z","msg":"一個二個蛋散老屈星如<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6ee3566670d43a1c2e27c6df1d85e7dec1793c66","tid":427680,"uid":124146,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"rep